I don't know what to think anymore.
It's like a dead end. 
Everything is almost like a dead end. 
I, however, don't want college to come.
I'm in love with a pot addict.
And I think I like a gay boy.
I've never been so confused in my life. 
I thought I had everything figured out,
but it just had to go and get complicated on me.
Everything's changing and I want it to stop.
What do I do?
Do I leave it up to God to let him sort it out?
Or do I try and fix it myself. 
I miss the easier days, when life seemed to end just because you mispelled a word in a spelling bee.
I miss the summer a lot.
I miss not talking to the people I used to share everything with.
I've gained one of them back, 
and I want him in the way I can't have him.
We tried it once and it didn't work.
But I want to try again, however
it won't happen... maybe it's just not meant to be.
Maybe I'm supposed to be finding someone else.
However, I like being stubborn and I don't want to find anyone else.
I'm being selfish and immature, I know.
It's just life and I should deal...right?
what if I'm not ready to do that?
I just want something good to happen to point me in the right direction...

So I'm sick of it all. Sick of all of it. I can't wait for my fucking vacation I don't care that it's only for 2 days I don't care. The only thing I care is getting away from here. The state. getting away from the drama. Every where I turn there's the drama and I seem to create it all. So fuck it. I need to get away. It hasn't been much of a summer vacation. The first couple weeks were fun and now it's hell. I need to go away and figure shit out. My life is pretty much fucked at the moment and nothing makes sense. Nothings working out like it should. I should have my license by now, but no, no one trusts me enough. I should have a car. I should have people I can count on. To rely on to make me happy but I don't. Not today maybe tomorrow but I doubt it. Everybody's moving on, with jobs, with life and here I am waving goodbye to them. Goodbye life. I'll see you again maybe in twenty years!!! My lifes passing me by and nothing to show for it, except a better relationship with my brother who is 3... pathetic I know. See why I am looking forward to vacation? 
Maybe I should just go to sleep and not wake up for a while like not wake until tuesday morning in time to leave! Wouldn't that be a medical miracle? Well I'm out no more blogging fun for me.

SO I am updating, It's been a while for a real update. It's kind of good, though, it's muchly needed. So yeah. It was raining and now it has stopped which is a shame. I <3 rain. Rain is perhaps the best thing on earth. :) It's supposed to rain some more later, and I can't wait. School's out, officially seniors. I'm not that excited. I have waited about 5 years for this to come and I'm not really ecstatic about it like some people are. It's too much to think about. I'm really sick of summer though and it's only just started. Whatever, it will end soon enough. 

Do you ever remember what it was like to be young and not worry about anything?

I went to go pick up my brother from daycare yesterday and I seen all these little kids just happy to be playing with each other and it was such a 'I wish I was young' kind of moment. I know you can't stay young forever, but I would like to go back and visit for a while. To not have to think about anything and just enjoy the time. It's probably something we all could use. Never have to worry about answering questions that you don't know the answers to, or can't find the answers for. You could just make it up and it was ok, because you were young and had  very little knowledge of life and what it really is like, all the hardships and the decisions. I just want to be done with all of it. Some days I feel like there is nobody or nothing there to help me make it through. Other days there's too many people there telling me different things and it's never what I want to hear. I just want that one person to be there and help me with things no one else can, and make those things better that no one else can.

Definitely made it up so anyways I get home and decided I wanted to leave so I left and came back sunday in time for practice so I went and we were doing goal post throws and I was throwing one and sarah was shagging at the end field and I went to go pick up one of the disks she threw and she threw another one and it hit me in the back ooooooh boy did that hurt, it still hurts, I am hoping it will bruise that would be awesome!!!!!
